Class::Gomor
============

DESCRIPTION

   This module is yet another class builder. This one adds parameter
   checking in the new() constructor, that is to check for attributes 
   existence, and definedness.

INSTALLATION

   To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

